column1: # Table of load Green's functions for a unit point load of mass (1 kg)
# uG_ReCalc:     vertical displacement evaluated by load Love numbers provided by Pagiatakis (1990)
# uG_SAL:        vertical displacement of the seafloor relative to the geoid (Vinogradova et al. 2015)
# Pagiatakis (1990) The response of a realistic earth to ocean tide loading
# Na and Baek (2011) Computation of the load Love number and the load Green's function for an elastic and spherically symmetric earth
# Vinogradova et al. (2015) Dynamic adjustment of the ocean circulation to self-attraction and loading effects
